text: The Rise of Catherine the Great also known as Catherine the Great is a 1934 British historical drama movie directed by Paul Czinner and starring Douglas Fairbanks, Jr., Elisabeth Bergner, Flora Robson, Gerald du Maurier, Dorothy Hale, Diana Napier, Irene Vanbrugh, Griffith Jones. It was distributed by United Artists. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1934 drama movies Category:1930s historical movies Category:British drama movies Category:Movies set in the 18th century Category:Movies set in Saint Petersburg Category:Movies based on plays Category:Movies directed by Paul Czinner
